🌏 SHEIN Cares For Animals 🌏

SHEIN is on a mission to protect the animals! Since we share the same home, we should consider animals our friends and do what we can to keep them safe. Let's join together to keep our animals protected!

The more we understand, the more ways we can have to help. That's why we created a fun game to help you learn more about the world's most adorable creatures.

For your chance to WIN 💚:⁣⁣⁣
🐬 Follow @sheinofficial & like this post.
🐧 Comment on your favorite animal emoji. (🐘, 🦘, 🦓, 🦒....)
🦏 Share the pic during the interactive game in the APP '#SHEINcares For Animals' as an IG post with the hashtag #SHEINcares

🔗 https://shein.top/e0vkp0l

Prizes:⁠
𝙂𝙧𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙋𝙧𝙞𝙯𝙚: $𝟱𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨 * 𝟳
